#. type: Content of: <h2>
msgid "Why Free Software needs Free Documentation"
msgstr "چرا نرم افزار آزاد نیاز به مستندات آزاد دارد"

#. type: Content of: <blockquote><p>
msgid ""
"<a href=\"http://defectivebydesign.org/ebooks.html\">Join our mailing list "
